      <title>在经济衰退的早期迹象中，美国失业率将上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/us-unemployment-rate-to-tick-up-amid-early-signs-of-recession</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博经济研究公司称，周五到期的美国劳工统计局月度报告将显示，随着经济开始陷入衰退，美国 11 月份失业率小幅上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/us-unemployment-rate-to-tick-up-amid-early-signs-of-recession</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
